      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0009",
      "text": "Read Timeout Value (RTV)",
      "bbox": [
        133.84,
        238.97,
        258.74,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0010",
      "text": "4.2.11.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.97,
        192.63,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0011",
      "text": "The RTV ELS requests an FC_Port to return the R_A_TOV and the E_D_TOV in the LS_ACC. The",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.03,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0012",
      "text": "LS_ACC returns the value that the FC_Port uses for R_T_TOV.  This provides the FC_Port transmit-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.0,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0013",
      "text": "ting the RTV ELS with information regarding these values from another FC_Port.  Usage of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.02,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0014",
      "text": "R_A_TOV, E_D_TOV and R_T_TOV requirements are given in FC-FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        419.22,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p054_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.11.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        178.22,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
